{"type":"message","id":"038dd662","parentId":"a04f6c7a","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:07:52.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好，我现在看到了各个 workspace 的技能分布。默认 workspace 的 skills 目录有以下技能：\n- academic-deep-research（✓ 只在默认 workspace）\n- ai-agent-helper（✓ 只在默认 workspace）\n- automation-workflows（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- capability-evolver（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- ddg-search-cli（✓ 只在默认 workspace）\n- deep-research-pro（✓ 只在默认 workspace）\n- find-skills（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- github（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- gog（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- imap-smtp-email（✓ 在 tech-lead 有，但其他没有）\n- multi-search-engine（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- proactive-agent（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- self-improving-agent（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- skill-vetter（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n- tavily-search（✓ 已在多个 workspace）\n\n需要同步的新技能：\n1. academic-deep-research\n2. ai-agent-helper\n3. ddg-search-cli\n4. deep-research-pro\n5. imap-smtp-email（tech-lead 已有，但其他没有）\n\n让我创建一个脚本来同步这些技能到所有 agents 的 workspace。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我看到了当前的情况。默认 workspace (`/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`) 有以下技能，需要同步到其他智能体的 workspace：\n\n**需要同步的新技能：**\n1. academic-deep-research\n2. ai-agent-helper\n3. ddg-search-cli\n4. deep-research-pro\n5. imap-smtp-email（已在 tech-lead，但其他没有）\n\n让我创建一个同步脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-9422277ef45e8171","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/sync-skills-to-all-agents.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n\n# 同步默认 workspace 的所有技能到所有智能体 workspace\nset -e\n\nDEFAULT_SKILLS_DIR=\"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/skills\"\nTARGET_WORKSPACES=(\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-main\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-ceo\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-cto\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-lanji\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-moyan\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-pm\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-researcher\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-tech-lead\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-weice\"\n    \"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace-yuanzhan\"\n)\n\n# 计数器\nSUCCESS_COUNT=0\nSKIP_COUNT=0\nERROR_COUNT=0\n\necho \"====================================\"\necho \"开始同步技能到所有智能体 workspace\"\necho \"====================================\"\necho \"\"\n\nfor target_dir in \"${TARGET_WORKSPACES[@]}\"; do\n    target_skills_dir=\"$target_dir/skills\"\n    workspace_name=$(basename \"$target_dir\")\n\n    echo \"处理: $workspace_name\"\n\n    # 创建 skills 目录（如果不存在）\n    if [ ! -d \"$target_skills_dir\" ]; then\n        mkdir -p \"$target_skills_dir\"\n        echo \"  ✓ 创建 skills 目录\"\n    fi\n\n    # 遍历默认 workspace 的所有技能\n    for skill_dir in \"$DEFAULT_SKILLS_DIR\"/*; do\n        if [ -d \"$skill_dir\" ]; then\n            skill_name=$(basename \"$skill_dir\")\n            target_skill_dir=\"$target_skills_dir/$skill_name\"\n\n            # 检查目标位置是否已存在\n            if [ -d \"$target_skill_dir\" ]; then\n                # 使用 rsync 比较差异并更新\n                if [ -n \"$(diff -rq \"$skill_dir\" \"$target_skill_dir\" 2>/dev/null)\" ]; then\n                    echo \"  ⚠ 更新现有技能: $skill_name\"\n                    rsync -av --delete \"$skill_dir/\" \"$target_skill_dir/\" > /dev/null 2>&1\n                    ((SUCCESS_COUNT++))\n                else\n                    echo \"  ⊙ 跳过（已同步）: $skill_name\"\n                    ((SKIP_COUNT++))\n                fi\n            else\n                echo \"  » 同步新技能: $skill_name\"\n                cp -r \"$skill_dir\" \"$target_skill_dir\"\n                ((SUCCESS_COUNT++))\n            fi\n        fi\n    done\n\n    echo \"\"\ndone\n\necho \"====================================\"\necho \"同步完成\"\necho \"====================================\"\necho \"成功同步: $SUCCESS_COUNT 项\"\necho \"跳过（已最新）: $SKIP_COUNT 项\"\necho \"错误: $ERROR_COUNT 项\"\necho \"\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":31386,"output":1023,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32409,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772762845334}}
