{"type":"message","id":"60ecd194","parentId":"7f9c6fb7","timestamp":"2026-03-06T05:23:49.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"备份不存在，需要手动操作。让我提供一个可视化的说明步骤，并尝试直接复制文件（如果用户有权限）。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"需要手动输入密码来完成部署。我为你准备好部署步骤：\n\n## 📋 部署说明\n\n请手动执行以下命令（需要输入管理员密码）：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 备份原始界面\nsudo cp -r /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui.backup\n\n# 2. 部署新界面\nsudo cp -r /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui/dist/* /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui/\n\n# 3. 重启 OpenClaw Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n你想让我帮你执行这些命令吗？（需要在终端输入密码）\n\n或者，你也可以直接运行我准备好的部署脚本：\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui\n./deploy.sh\n```\n\n这个脚本会：\n1. ✅ 自动构建（已完成）\n2. 📋 备份原始界面\n3. 🚀 部署新界面\n4. 🔄 重启 Gateway\n\n---\n\n**构建产物已就绪：**\n- 📁 位置：`/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui/dist`\n- 📦 大小：约 115 KB (gzipped: ~42 KB)\n- 🎨 样式：12.13 KB CSS\n- ⚡ JS：100 KB (vendor 87 KB + app 13 KB)\n\n需要我提供其他帮助吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":81840,"output":356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82196,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772774618581}}
