{"type":"message","id":"25b06e34","parentId":"5d4b6483","timestamp":"2026-03-06T05:29:08.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"原始界面有一个大的 JS 文件。让我更新我的前端，添加完整的 OpenClaw 功能。\n\n我需要：\n1. 添加左侧边栏导航\n2. 添加各种视图页面：\n   - Dashboard/Overview\n   - Agents（智能体列表）\n   - Sessions（会话列表）\n   - Configs（配置文件）\n   - Logs（日志）\n   - Status（状态）\n3. 连接到真实的 OpenClaw Gateway API\n4. 实现所有的路由和状态管理\n\n让我重写整个前端结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-856e6f4e9eb99fe4","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"<template>\n  <div id=\"app\" class=\"app-container\">\n    <div class=\"background-effects\">\n      <div class=\"gradient-orb orb-1\"></div>\n      <div class=\"gradient-orb orb-2\"></div>\n      <div class=\"gradient-orb orb-3\"></div>\n      <div class=\"particle-container\" id=\"particles\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"glass-panel\">\n      <!-- 侧边栏 -->\n      <aside class=\"sidebar\">\n        <div class=\"sidebar-header\">\n          <div class=\"logo-container\">\n            <div class=\"logo-icon\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"45\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\"/>\n                <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"35\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\"/>\n                <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"25\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\"/>\n                <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"15\" fill=\"currentColor\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h1 class=\"logo-text\">\n              <span>Open</span>Claw\n            </h1>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <nav class=\"sidebar-nav\">\n          <router-link to=\"/dashboard\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">📊</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">概览</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/agents\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">🤖</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">智能体</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/sessions\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">💬</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">会话</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/session-create\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">➕</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">新建会话</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <div class=\"nav-divider\"></div>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/configs\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">⚙️</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">配置</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/logs\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">📄</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">日志</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/status\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">🔧</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">系统状态</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n\n          <router-link to=\"/tools\" custom v-slot=\"{ navigate, isActive }\">\n            <button :class=\"['nav-item', { active: isActive }]\" @click=\"navigate\">\n              <span class=\"nav-icon\">🧰</span>\n              <span class=\"nav-label\">工具</span>\n            </button>\n          </router-link>\n        </nav>\n\n        <div class=\"sidebar-footer\">\n          <div class=\"status-indicator\" :class=\"connectionStatus\">\n            <span class=\"status-dot\"></span>\n            <span class=\"status-text\">{{ statusText }}</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"footer-info\">\n            <span class=\"version\">v1.0</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </aside>\n\n      <!-- 主内容区 -->\n      <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <!-- 顶部状态栏 -->\n        <header class=\"top-bar\">\n          <div class=\"top-bar-left\">\n            <h2 class=\"page-title\">{{ currentPageTitle }}</h2>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"top-bar-right\">\n            <div class=\"api-status\">\n              <span class=\"status-label\">Gateway:</span>\n              <span class=\"status-value\" :class=\"connectionStatus\">● {{ statusText }}</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </header>\n\n        <!-- 路由内容 -->\n        <div class=\"content-area\">\n          <router-view></router-view>\n        </div>\n      </main>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup>\nimport { ref, computed, onMounted } from 'vue'\nimport { useRoute } from 'vue-router'\n\nconst route = useRoute()\n\n// 状态\nconst connectionStatus = ref('connected')\n\n// 计算属性\nconst statusText = computed(() => {\n  const statusMap = {\n    connected: '已连接',\n    connecting: '连接中...',\n    disconnected: '未连接'\n  }\n  return statusMap[connectionStatus.value] || '未知'\n})\n\nconst currentPageTitle = computed(() => {\n  const titles = {\n    '/dashboard': '概览',\n    '/agents': '智能体管理',\n    '/sessions': '会话列表',\n    '/session-create': '新建会话',\n    '/configs': '配置文件',\n    '/logs': '系统日志',\n    '/status': '系统状态',\n    '/tools': '工具管理'\n  }\n  return titles[route.path] || 'OpenClaw 控制台'\n})\n\n// 粒子效果\nconst initParticles = () => {\n  const container = document.getElementById('particles')\n  if (!container) return\n\n  for (let i = 0; i < 30; i++) {\n    const particle = document.createElement('div')\n    particle.className = 'particle'\n    particle.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + '%'\n    particle.style.top = Math.random() * 100 + '%'\n    particle.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 5 + 's'\n    particle.style.animationDuration = (Math.random() * 3 + 2) + 's'\n    container.appendChild(particle)\n  }\n}\n\n// 生命周期\nonMounted(() => {\n  initParticles()\n})\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.app-container {\n  width: 100vw;\n  height: 100vh;\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n/* 背景效果 */\n.background-effects {\n  position: fixed;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  z-index: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.gradient-orb {\n  position: absolute;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  filter: blur(60px);\n  opacity: 0.6;\n  animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n\n.orb-1 {\n  width: 500px;\n  height: 500px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  top: -200px;\n  left: -200px;\n  animation-delay: 0s;\n}\n\n.orb-2 {\n  width: 600px;\n  height: 600px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  bottom: -300px;\n  right: -200px;\n  animation-delay: 2s;\n}\n\n.orb-3 {\n  width: 400px;\n  height: 400px;\n  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);\n  top: 50%;\n  left: 50%;\n  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n  animation-delay: 4s;\n}\n\n@keyframes float {\n  0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }\n  33% { transform: translate(30px, -30px); }\n  66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px); }\n}\n\n.particle-container {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n}\n\n.particle {\n  position: absolute;\n  width: 4px;\n  height: 4px;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  animation: rise linear infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes rise {\n  0% {\n    transform: translateY(100vh) scale(0);\n    opacity: 0;\n  }\n  50% {\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n  100% {\n    transform: translateY(-100px) scale(1);\n    opacity: 0;\n  }\n}\n\n/* 毛玻璃面板 */\n.glass-panel {\n  position: relative;\n  z-index: 1;\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  display: flex;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);\n  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n}\n\n/* 侧边栏 */\n.sidebar {\n  width: 280px;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n\n.sidebar-header {\n  padding: 24px 20px;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n}\n\n.logo-container {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 12px;\n}\n\n.logo-icon {\n  width: 40px;\n  height: 40px;\n  color: #E60012;\n  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes pulse {\n  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }\n  50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }\n}\n\n.logo-text {\n  font-size: 22px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #E60012 100%);\n  -webkit-background-clip: text;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n  background-clip: text;\n  letter-spacing: -0.5px;\n}\n\n.logo-text span {\n  color: #ffffff;\n  -webkit-text-fill-color: #ffffff;\n}\n\n/* 侧边栏导航 */\n.sidebar-nav {\n  flex: 1;\n  padding: 16px 12px;\n  overflow-y: auto;\n}\n\n.nav-item {\n  width: 100%;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 12px;\n  padding: 12px 16px;\n  border: none;\n  background: transparent;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  text-align: left;\n  margin-bottom: 4px;\n}\n\n.nav-item:hover {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  color: white;\n}\n\n.nav-item.active {\n  background: rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.2);\n  color: white;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(230, 0, 18, 0.3);\n}\n\n.nav-icon {\n  font-size: 18px;\n  min-width: 24px;\n}\n\n.nav-divider {\n  height: 1px;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  margin: 16px 0;\n}\n\n/* 侧边栏底部 */\n.sidebar-footer {\n  padding: 16px 20px 20px;\n  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n}\n\n.status-indicator {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 8px;\n  padding: 10px 16px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n.status-indicator.connected .status-dot {\n  background: #00ff88;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 8px #00ff88;\n}\n\n.status-indicator.connecting .status-dot {\n  background: #ffaa00;\n  animation: blink 0.5s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n\n.status-indicator.disconnected .status-dot {\n  background: #ff3366;\n}\n\n@keyframes blink {\n  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n  50% { opacity: 0.3; }\n}\n\n.status-dot {\n  width: 8px;\n  height: 8px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: #00ff88;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 8px #00ff88;\n}\n\n.footer-info {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\n}\n\n.version {\n  padding: 2px 8px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E60012, #ff3366);\n  color: white;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n/* 主内容区 */\n.main-content {\n  flex: 1;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n/* 顶部栏 */\n.top-bar {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  padding: 16px 24px;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n}\n\n.page-title {\n  font-size: 24px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: white;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.api-status {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 8px;\n  padding: 8px 16px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\n\n.status-label {\n  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n}\n\n.status-value {\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n.status-value.connected {\n  color: #00ff88;\n}\n\n.status-value.connecting {\n  color: #ffaa00;\n}\n\n.status-value.disconnected {\n  color: #ff3366;\n}\n\n/* 内容区 */\n.content-area {\n  flex: 1;\n  overflow-y: auto;\n  padding: 24px;\n}\n\n/* 滚动条样式 */\n.sidebar-nav::-webkit-scrollbar,\n.content-area::-webkit-scrollbar {\n  width: 6px;\n}\n\n.sidebar-nav::-webkit-scrollbar-track,\n.content-area::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n}\n\n.sidebar-nav::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb,\n.content-area::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n  border-radius: 3px;\n}\n\n.sidebar-nav::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover,\n.content-area::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n}\n</style>","path":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui/src/App.vue"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":82699,"output":3811,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772774824083}}
