{"type":"message","id":"b077d0c1","parentId":"ca241d92","timestamp":"2026-03-06T05:46:54.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！构建成功了！虽然有警告但是不影响使用。现在所有组件都已创建好，构建完成。我需要总结一下给用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **构建成功！**\n\n## 🎉 OpenClaw 中国联通风格 UI 已完成\n\n### 已创建的功能模块\n\n**左侧导航栏：**\n- 📊 **概览** - 系统统计和快速操作\n- 🤖 **智能体** - 查看和管理所有智能体（9个）\n- 💬 **会话** - 查看和搜索历史会话\n- ➕ **新建会话** - 选择智能体创建新会话\n- ⚙️ **配置文件** - 查看 openclaw.json 等配置\n- 📄 **日志** - 系统日志查看和过滤\n- 🔧 **系统状态** - Gateway 和系统信息\n- 🧰 **工具管理** - 启用/禁用各种工具\n\n### 构建产物\n\n```\n✓ built in 1.82s\n\n文件大小：\n- index.html: 2.36 kB (gzipped: 1.06 kB)\n- 总 JS: 119 KB (gzipped: 46 KB)\n- 总 CSS: 32 KB (gzipped: 11 kB)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 现在可以部署了！\n\n需要我帮你部署到 OpenClaw Gateway 吗？\n\n部署命令（需要管理员密码）：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 备份原始界面\nsudo cp -r /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui.backup\n\n# 2. 部署新界面\nsudo cp -r /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui/dist/* /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui/\n\n# 3. 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者你也可以直接运行部署脚本：\n\n```bash\ncd /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui\n./deploy.sh\n```\n\n要我现在执行部署吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":110024,"output":451,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110475,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772776000681}}
