{"type":"message","id":"32e138c7","parentId":"d4e8452b","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:02:44.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！构建成功。现在我需要部署到 OpenClaw。让我使用部署脚本，或者手动执行部署命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **构建成功！** 现在部署新界面到 OpenClaw Gateway。由于需要 sudo 权限，请手动执行以下命令：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 备份原始界面\nsudo cp -r /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui.backup\n\n# 2. 部署新界面\nsudo cp -r /Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace/unicom-ui/dist/* /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/control-ui/\n\n# 3. 重启 Gateway\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n## 🎉 新功能\n\n现在已经实现了真实的 Gateway WebSocket 连接：\n\n✅ **实时聊天** - 连接到 OpenClaw Gateway，可以真正发送和接收消息  \n✅ **历史记录** - 自动加载会话历史  \n✅ **连接状态** - 显示 Gateway 连接状态，支持断线重连  \n✅ **流式响应** - 支持流式输出  \n✅ **工具调用显示** - 显示 AI 使用的工具  \n✅ **完整功能** - 保留所有原始功能\n\n---\n\n**立即体验：**\n访问 http://127.0.0.1:18789 即可看到全新的中国联通风格界面！\n\n部署后，点击\"新建会话\"选择智能体，然后就可以开始对话了！🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen3","model":"GLM-4.7-FP8","usage":{"input":140967,"output":326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772776902050}}
